Lu Yang.

291
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,400
Do you know what shameless is?

292
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:08,250
I can't be more shameless than you.

293
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,120
I see.

294
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:13,000
You just want to make more money, right?

295
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,820
How about this?

296
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,820
Go and follow this person.

297
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:24,720
This time, I'm going to prepare a big gift.

298
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:27,360
Zhang Yan.

299
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:28,520
Here,

300
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,050
have some water.

301
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,440
Thank you.

302
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,120
Here is the thing.

303
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:34,720
Zhang Yan.

304
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:38,080
We still need to verify some information with you.

305
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,960
Your husband's name and height.

306
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:40,820
And his weight.

307
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:42,820
His name is Tian Liang.

308
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,560
He is 1.82 meters tall,

309
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:47,520
and weighs about 90 kg.

310
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,620
When did he go missing?

311
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,240
About 5 days ago.

312
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,060
You don't know the exact time?

313
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:57,520
He usually stays at the gym.

314
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:59,740
We don't contact each other much.

315
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,880
Then when was the last time you contacted him?

316
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:03,960
The last time

317
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,720
was about a week ago.

318
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:08,440
It's been a week and you just came to report it?

319
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:10,640
I went to the gym to look for him last time

320
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,500
and found out he didn't go to work.

321
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,680
Zhang Yan,

322
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,520
let me ask you.

323
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:18,940
Did Tian Liang have any valuables on him?

324
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,880
Valuables?

325
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:21,840
Mobile phone,

326
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,280
bank cards,

327
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,120
and a watch.

328
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,500
Take a look.

329
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:29,880
Among these watches,

330
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,410
is Tian Liang's watch here?

331
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:41,480
He seems to have a watch like this.

332
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,200
He treasures it very much.

333
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,860
I haven't seen it much either.

334
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,320
I think so.

335
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,080
Are you sure

336
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,140
this one is his?

337
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,970
I'm not sure either.

338
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:58,130
Tian Liang is just an ordinary fitness coach.

339
00:13:58,280 --> 00:14:00,010
He couldn't afford this watch.

340
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:02,880
That watch of his,

341
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:05,010
it was bought for him by a woman.

342
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:05,400
Well,

343
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:06,360
Zhang Yan,

344
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,400
let me ask you,

345
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:10,250
what is the main source of income for your family?

346
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:12,360
Tian Liang is a fitness coach.

347
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:14,400
I work in a clothing factory.

348
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,980
What about your spending?

349
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:19,650
His monthly salary is about five or six thousand.

350
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:22,650
There's not much left after paying the mortgage.

351
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:23,840
If that's the case,

352
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,480
it doesn't match the information we have.

353
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,410
As far as we know,

354
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,480
Tian Liang has changed to a car worth hundreds of thousands

355
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:31,080
and frequently visits bars.

356
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,610
Where did he get all that money?

357
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,120
He said

358
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,880
he made some rich friend.

359
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,490
Do you know them?

360
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:39,720
No, I don't.

361
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,400
When I asked him,

362
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,520
he would hit me

363
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,940
and swear at me.

364
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:45,480
Honey.

365
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:47,000
Don't touch me.

366
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,610
You reek of alcohol.

367
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:51,640
Do you like it?

368
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,100
Here you go.

369
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,100
I don't want it.

370
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:59,120
Which woman gave this to you?

371
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:01,060
I'm giving it to you, just take it.

372
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,200
Who told you to leave?

373
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:11,200
Take it.

374
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:18,320
With this face I have now,

375
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:20,890
as long as you follow me,

376
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:24,410
I'll definitely give you endless money to spend.

377
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:25,840
Okay,

378
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,980
we have recorded your situation.

379
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,520
I will contact you if anything comes up.

380
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,720
That's all for today.

381
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:31,720
Okay.

382
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:32,560
Xiaoshuang,

383
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,220
see her out.

384
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:36,280
Thank you.

385
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,020
No problem.

386
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,200
Zhang Yan.

387
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,420
Speak of the devil.

388
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:46,920
Now we can apply to the chief.

389
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,650
Let's go to Tian Liang's house.

390
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:51,840
Is your mentor always this serious?

391
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,240
Can we go now?

392
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,060
Mentor.

393
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,160
I was wondering,

394
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:58,890
why didn't you let her identify the body just now?

395
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,800
Is there anything in your head?

396
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,860
Your mentor didn't want to alert her.

397
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,890
If we lack useful evidence,

398
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:07,120
and she finds out her husband is dead,

399
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,580
what if she drops the case?

400
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,680
The most important thing right now

401
00:16:10,680 --> 00:16:12,210
is to find Tian Liang's DNA.

402
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:14,690
Don't tell anyone I'm your mentor.

403
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,010
Let's go.

404
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,460
You can learn from me instead.

405
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:20,200
No.

406
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,130
Wait for me, Master.

407
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,930
Destroy all the photos.

408
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:28,410
Don't let the police find any connection.

409
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:28,960
Got it.

410
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:31,400
Any movement on his end?

411
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:32,720
Not yet.

412
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:34,960
About this incident,

413
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:36,740
find out the truth.

414
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:37,560
Okay.

415
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:38,440
Got it.
